Andy Murray takes on potential banana skin Grigor Dimitrov on Centre Court as the Briton continues the defence of his Wimbledon crown.

He will be followed up on the showpiece court by Roger Federer, who takes on Stanislas Wawrinka, with Simona Halep opening play against Sabine Lisicki.

Elsewhere, Eugenie Bouchard and Novak Djokovic are both in action on Court One.

